These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, traveling, chess, drawing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, action, zombie, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, weightlifting, skateboarding, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bus, subway, tram
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
 2. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
 3. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
 5. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person driving the train##8
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 8. the person watching scientific movies is between the person driving the bus and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 9. the person driving the tram is the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
13. the person watching zombie movies is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
14. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person driving the subway##1
15. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking     | traveling   | drawing | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | action | scientific   | disaster   | zombie  |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | skateboarding  | snowboarding  | volleyball |
| Transport     | train    | subway | bus     | tram    |

