.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, juice, coffee
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, lemon, pepper
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, blues, folk, gospel
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hedgehog, goat, pony
 1. the fan of folk is between the owner of the turtle and the fan of blues##2
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
 4. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
 5. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the fan of blues##8
 6. the person eating pepper is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
 8. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of d&b is the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
11. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
14. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
15. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
17. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
18. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
19. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | 7up | juice | coffee  | soy-milk  |
| Food          | pepper     | cabbage | asparagus | lemon  |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | folk  | gospel | d&b |
| Pet           | goat | pony | turtle    | hedgehog  |

