.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, singing, fishing, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, adventure, sports, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, dubstep, house, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, baseball, rowing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
 7. the fan of house is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | gardening    | magic-tricks   | fishing | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts     | sports  | epic   | adventure      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | salsa    | house      | techno       |
| Sport         | rowing    | tennis | volleyball   | baseball    |

