 3. the person eating pepper is the chef##1
 4. the person eating grapefruit is between the coach and the accountant##2
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the right of the person eating grapefruit##8
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the paramedic##1
10. the accountant is the person who's sport is rugby##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person eating eggplant##8
12. the coach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
14. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
15. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
