 4. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 5. the person driving the boat is the polish##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the italian##8
 7. the person drinking milk is not the french##6
 8. the photographer is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person drinking milk##7
 9. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
10. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the photographer##3
11. the videographer is on the right of the dancer##1
12. the photographer is not the australian##6
13. the italian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
14. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
15. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the photographer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
