 9. the engineer is on the far left or far right##3
10. the teacher is not to the left of the teacher##8
11. the engineer is on the far left##1
12. the lawyer is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the boat is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
15. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
