 1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 8. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
 9. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
10. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the fan of r&b##8
11. the fan of country is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite   | hot-chocolate     | soy-milk    | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | electronic      | country     | r&b     |
| Sport         | biathlon | soccer  | swimming     | rugby  |
| Transport     | train     | ship | helicopter | subway     |

