.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, coffee, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, traveling, singing, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, country
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, japanese, indian, canadian
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the canadian##1
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
 3. the person drinking 7up is the fan of funk##1
 4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the indian##3
 9. the japanese is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
10. the fan of jazz is not the argentine##6
11. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
12. the canadian is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
13. the fan of country is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
14. the argentine is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
