 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
 6. the person driving the roller is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the scientist is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
 8. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
 9. the firefighter is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
10. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
12. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
13. the person driving the helicopter is not to the left of the scientist##8

