 6. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 8. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
10. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the designer##7
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

