.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, filmmaking, rock-climbing, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, architect, lawyer, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, superhero, musical
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, disco, soul, gospel
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the mechanic##8
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 3. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
 4. the chef is the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the lawyer##6
 6. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the fan of disco##8
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the lawyer##8
 8. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 9. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
10. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
11. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the lawyer and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking    | rock-climbing   | reading   | filmmaking |
| Job           | mechanic | architect    | lawyer | chef    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | family | fantasy     | musical    |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | soul      | disco         | gospel     |

 